cz.cvut.fel.webrtc.db

Class WebRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cvut.fel.webrtc.db.WebRegistry

  • public class WebRegistry
extends Object
    Map of users registered in the system. This class has a concurrent hash map to store users, using its name as key in the map.
    Since:
    4.3.1
    Author:
    Boni Garcia (bgarcia@gsyc.es), Micael Gallego (micael.gallego@gmail.com), Ivan Gracia (izanmail@gmail.com)
